Package: BPNonceAcceptability
Type: Package
Title: Acceptability Judgments for Brazilian Portuguese Nonce Words
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",   family = "Nguyen",  role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "david@example.com"),
    person(given = "Rosser",  family = "Martin", role = "aut",          email = "rosser@example.com")
Description: 
    Functions and data for analyzing how word structure (syllable length 
    and initial segment type) influences nonce‐word acceptability judgments 
    in Brazilian Portuguese. Includes plotting utilities (mosaic plots) 
    and statistical tests.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0),
    ggmosaic (>= 0.2.2)
